original_title: Bareback Auditions 13: New Faces, New Wood
overview: There are several NEW FACES and NEW WOOD among the Lucas Men these days, and now is your chance to get to know them in BAREBACK AUDITIONS 13! Nico Zetta is the breakout star of the movie, appearing in three scenes, the first of which has him sharing Vlad Stark's ass with Pol Prince. Afterward, he goes one-on-one with Ricky Hard. Then Nico teams up with Rafael Carreras to pound Isaac X and Joaquin Santana. Also featured is Sir Peter and Tomas Brand spit-roasting Jonas Jackson in a fantasy game show scenario!
title: Bareback Auditions 13: New Faces, New Wood
